{"tid":2004061,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"人權新聞獎揭盅 香港電台奪兩大獎四優異獎","createTime":"2020-05-06T08:02:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-06T09:22:53.000Z","uid":240362,"like":63,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"d12b3796fa70ae88e47e1dc82bacd8ddf872d858","tid":2004061,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T08:02:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1524540-20200506.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1524540-20200506.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=HVlUx73Us%2FxglV2o%2BMpWBbP2tejZlako6KwT%2FyznMNw%3D&h=755fbae2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1524540-20200506.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=11822544\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1524540-20200506.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1524540_2_L_20200506152826.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1524540_2_L_20200506152826.jpg&h=c500237e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第24屆人權新聞獎今日揭盅，香港電台在不同組別共奪得6個獎項，包括2個大奬及4個優異獎。<br />\n<br />\n新聞部記者李大煒及汪溟曦聯合製作的《出理大記》奪得「電台廣播和錄音組別」大獎。新聞部記者仇志榮的作品《羈押新彊再教育營 事主談及被虐經歷》在同一組別，獲優異獎。<br />\n<br />\n新聞部視像新聞組記者葉真真及盧珮珊聯合製作的《快遞公司禁運風波》，獲得「短片組別」的優異獎。<br />\n<br />\n《鏗鏘集：反修例運動系列》獲「紀錄片（中文）組別」大獎。《視點31：中國大數據生活系列》獲同組別的優異獎。唐若韞製作的《在那不存在的監獄內》奪「紀錄片（英文）組別」優異獎。<br />\n<br />\n今屆人權新聞獎共收到488份參賽作品，數目為歷年之冠，多個本地及國際媒體參與，不少得獎作品與去年本港反修例示威有關。人權新聞獎由香港外國記者會、國際特赦組織香港分會及香港記者協會合辦。因應新型肺炎疫情持續，頒獎禮延期舉行。"},{"pid":"dea2ebcfed642aa7405a2961540ddfb9c69a4957","tid":2004061,"uid":310700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T08:03:04.000Z","msg":"G持清"},{"pid":"192abf0ef2cc07bacff907c5db64506734489aad","tid":2004061,"uid":240362,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T08:04:30.000Z","msg":"重溫《出理大記》第一集：留守者冒險爬渠 逃脫後仍恐被捕疑有幻聽<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1498064-20191217.htm?archive_date=2019-12-17\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1498064-20191217.htm%3Farchive_date%3D2019-12-17&d=HVlUx73Us%2FxglV2o%2BMpWBbP2tejZlako6KwT%2FyznMNw%3D&h=2b7e5323\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1498064-20191217.htm%3Farchive_date%3D2019-12-17&h=4fac3c87\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1498064-20191217.htm?archive_date=2019-12-17</a><br />\n重溫《出理大記》第二集：和理非組車隊營救 中學校長籲以愛止亂<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1498266-20191218.htm?archive_date=2019-12-18\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1498266-20191218.htm%3Farchive_date%3D2019-12-18&d=HVlUx73Us%2FxglV2o%2BMpWBbP2tejZlako6KwT%2FyznMNw%3D&h=40b07d71\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1498266-20191218.htm%3Farchive_date%3D2019-12-18&h=c937c0e5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1498266-20191218.htm?archive_date=2019-12-18</a><br />\n重溫《羈押新彊再教育營、事主談及被虐經歷》:<br />\n<a href=\"https://podcast.rthk.hk/podcast/item.php?pid=907&amp;eid=128319&amp;year=2019&amp;list=1&amp;lang=zh-CN\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpodcast.rthk.hk%2Fpodcast%2Fitem.php%3Fpid%3D907%26eid%3D128319%26year%3D2019%26list%3D1%26lang%3Dzh-CN&d=HVlUx73Us%2FxglV2o%2BMpWBbP2tejZlako6KwT%2FyznMNw%3D&h=ed6270a9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://podcast.rthk.hk/podcast/item.php?pid=907&amp;eid=128319&amp;year=2019&amp;list=1&amp;lang=zh-CN</a><br />\n重溫《快遞公司禁運風波》:<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1443915-20190220.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%